# Mosquitto ACL for the Frigate NVR stack.
#
# See contracts/mqtt-topics.md for the full contract. This ACL enforces:
#   - `frigate` has full access to frigate/# (it IS the publisher).
#   - `homeassistant` has read-only access to frigate/# plus write only to
#     the /set topics used for privacy-mode and runtime toggles.

user frigate
topic readwrite frigate/#

user homeassistant
topic read frigate/#
topic write frigate/+/detect/set
topic write frigate/+/recordings/set
topic write frigate/+/snapshots/set
topic write frigate/+/motion/set
